data.title: Alyson Stoner interview with Alloy.
data.meta_description: Camp Rock starlet Alyson Stoner interview with Alloy excerpts: Do you spend a lot of time with the Disney crew? Now that I did Camp Rock and Phineas and Ferb (the animated series I'm on), I go to a lot more events. Those opportunities for me to bond with the kids who are on the shows are great for…
